Package: sshoyu-server
Version: 7.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Denis <claude-devops@zerum.com>
Depends: bash, caddy, openssh-server, debconf (>= 0.5), adduser
Description: SShoyu SSH tunnel server
 Configures a server to accept reverse SSH tunnels and automatically manage
 Caddy reverse proxy subdomains. Installs sshoyu_cli.sh as a forced SSH
 command for a dedicated system user, and configures sudoers to allow safe
 Caddyfile manipulation and service reloading.
